# Implementation Review: eden-phase-8b-service-extraction

## Plan

- Path: `/Users/ericalt/Documents/eden/docs/plans/eden-phase-8b-service-extraction.md`
- Summary: Phase 8b finishes the cross-process reference deployment by extracting workers into independent subprocesses, landing the task-store-server and orchestrator CLI entrypoints, scaffolding shared-token auth as a reference-only extension, and proving the whole arrangement with a real-subprocess end-to-end test.

## Implementation files

