|---|---|---|
| `spec/v0/07-wire-protocol.md` | Modified — appended §12 "Reference-only extensions — authentication (informative)" | Spec addendum |
| `reference/packages/eden-dispatch/src/eden_dispatch/driver.py` | Modified — extracted `run_orchestrator_iteration`, kept `run_experiment` calling it | eden-dispatch refactor |
| `reference/packages/eden-dispatch/src/eden_dispatch/__init__.py` | Modified — re-export `run_orchestrator_iteration` | eden-dispatch refactor |
| `reference/packages/eden-dispatch/tests/test_orchestrator_iteration.py` | Created — 5 unit tests covering the orchestrator iteration in isolation | Tests §3 |
| `reference/packages/eden-wire/src/eden_wire/server.py` | Modified — added `shared_token` kwarg + middleware | Shared-token auth |
