   231	    """Poll-and-run evaluator worker.
   232	
   233	    Discovers pending ``evaluate`` tasks, reads the referenced trial,
   234	    runs its scripted evaluation, and submits. ``success`` and
   235	    ``error`` write metrics on the trial via the orchestrator's
